data.description: You can really have it all in this three bedroom, two bathroom brick-front home in Baltimore County, Maryland. Recently renovated from the bottom up, the interior of this home has been fully reimagined. Through the new porch, we arrive at the main floor where the living room, kitchen, and separate dining room reside. As you make your way into the charming living room, you are greeted with beautiful, refinished hardwood floors and brand new insulated and energy efficient windows. The dining room continues the trend of hardwood flooring, along with a ceiling lamp, while the gourmet kitchen contains elegant ceramic tile flooring and brand new granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. In the basement, you will find the new fully finished family room, recently carpeted from wall to wall, along with a full bathroom. Lying upstairs are three bedrooms, including the master bedroom, with ample space to house all your needs and wants, and windows to enjoy the natural sunlight. The home is freshly painted and has had new light fixtures installed throughout, and a fenced yard welcomes you at the back.For more information about Forest Park or to schedule a showing, contact Ellie McIntire at 443-418-7668, or email Ellie at Elliemcintire@mris.com.
